description:
I have a mamas & papas irbo stroller dor sale. I have used this stroller for 3 months now & it's still in excellent condition. This stroller is also a seat which you can sit the child & sit him in restaurant chairs as well. Perfectly well stroller. Reason I'm selling it is because I have 2 strollers.  
I am selling this stroller for 300 or better offer. PRICE IS NEGOTIABLE.

From busy city streets to winding country roads; from an afternoon feeding the ducks in the park to retail therapy - the VISTA takes your child on the road in style. Designed to grow with your child, the VISTA is the ideal strolling solution from birth through the toddler years. It adapts easily to your growing family with solutions for a big brother or sister. 
 
There's a lot for your little one to see -- get out there and get strolling! 
 
Bassinet: Suitable from birth to 6 months 
Toddler Seat: Suitable from 3 months to 50 lbs. 
Easy one-step fold--with or without the seat attached 
Welded and formed aircraft aluminum alloy frame 
Includes both bassinet and seat--completely interchangeable and requires no fabric swapping 
One-button handle-height adjustment 
Added rubber bumpers to protect the stroller handlebar in standing position 
Smooth-rolling "no-flat" foam and rubber wheels 
Elevated seat/bassinet height brings you closer to your child 
Removable bumper bar cover 
Floating arch "no kick" rear axle 
Red/green successful attachment indicators 
Convenient zip-in rain shield and mesh bug shield included 
Ventilated bassinet canopy and aerated mattress for air flow 
All-natural bassinet liner of cotton + soybean fiber 
Removable, washable and interchangeable fabric 
Easy to activate brake system 
Shock-absorbing front + rear suspension 
Stands when folded
VERY COOL VINTAGE BILT-RITE STROLLER.  MEASURES 23 INCHES HIGH.  MISSING CUSION INSIDE.

description:
We have an older basic Bugaboo infant bassinet stroller with frame, bassinet, canopy for sale in good preowned condition. A solid smooth riding stroller for $140 cash or best offer. 
Usually for babies 0-6 months. This stroller can be also adapted for babies to sit up with Chameleon seat fabric.  
 
What's included:  
 
-stroller frame with wheels 
-detachable seat 
-bassinet fabric (tan) 
-canopy fabric (tan) 
-detachable carry handle (needs new clips) 
 
Details: 
-has safety features including wrist strap and locking wheel lever by the handle 
-frame folds in half 
-infant bassinet detaches from the stroller frame so you can carry the baby in it with the carrying handle.  
-stroller converts to a sit up stroller if you switch in Chamaeleon fabric seat on the frame.  
 
Newer tires, rides smooth.  
 
Pick up by Cubesmart in Clinton Hill/Prospect Heights, near Fulton/Atlantic; Grand Ave 
 
Please email me if you're interested along with any questions, best times you can meet and your # mobile number; also whether you prefer phone or text.   
 
I respond quickly.  
 
Thanks!

padded, reclining seats

Product Details

Spot clean 
 
There is a tear on one of the seats, but I think it could easily be fixed with a curved needle and thread. Missing lid to adult tray.

Gently used BOB stroller.  Good condition.  From a smoke-free home 
 
With large inflatable tires that roll effortlessly over varied terrain, this collapsible sport stroller offers an adjustable reclining seat and a cushy suspension so everyone will enjoy the adventure. 
 
Details 
 
+ Made with a tough frame and durable fabric for lasting use; 2-step folding design supplies convenient transport and storage
